relevant_findings.general: Alert and oriented to person, place and situation; no apparent distress.
relevant_findings.HEENT: No trauma, pupils round and reactive to light and accommodation, no lymphadenopathy, oropharynx clear, no exudates, no icterus.
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, no murmurs/gallops/rubs.
relevant_findings.pulmonary: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no rales/crackles/rhonchi.
relevant_findings.gastrointestinal: Soft, mild epigastric tenderness, mildly distended; no guarding/rebound, bowel sounds present.
relevant_findings.extremities: No clubbing or cyanosis; 2+ distal pulses; peripheral IV present, trace edema bilaterally.
